<span id="freeTextContainer11313903405957434974">Now THIS is what I call a pleasant surprise. <br/><br/>I’m very tempted to jump right onto book two but<br/><br/>First order of business: recharge brain battery. <br/><br/>~~~~~~~~~&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;~~~~~~&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;~~~~~<br/><br/><br/>Let’s... DO THIS!<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1518042062ra/25022330.gif' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
