<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16000635928498602551">Steven Erikson is the pseudonym of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5363802.Steve_Rune_Lundin' rel='nofollow noopener'>Steve Rune Lundin</a>, a Canadian novelist, who was educated and trained as both an archaeologist and anthropologist. His best-known work is the series, the <i>Malazan Book of the Fallen</i>.<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://us.macmillan.com/author/stevenerikson'>http://us.macmillan.com/author/steven...</a></span>
